  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nIf you close the app with PNs enabled (so it closes but doesn't log out), change the theme on the device (light > dark), and then open the app, the theme will not be applied to the app.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTheme is applied\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTheme is not applied\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Enable PNs on Android device\r\n2. Close the app\r\n3. Change theme on the device\r\n4. Open the app\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/232508079-232f935e-58ca-44a9-a658-d43e6316e89a.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 17/04\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
